The paper deals with wireless communication and power transfer, which falls under the domain of information theory (cs.IT) and networked systems (cs.NI). The use of multiple antennas and MIMO technology suggests that the paper may also be relevant to multimedia systems (cs.MM) and communication engineering (cs.CE). Finally, the study of optimal transmission strategies and achievable rate-energy regions involves system optimization and control, which falls under the category of control systems (cs.SY).
